Title: Timshel
Writer: Joe Gayton (creator), Tony Gayton (creator), John Shiban, Jami O'Brien (executive story editor), Bruce Marshall Romans (staff writer)
Actors: Anson Mount, Colm Meaney, Common, Dominique McElligott
Plot: Cullen and the search party find the natives who attacked the surveyor's camp and later derailed a train; Elam and Eva discuss their future, before getting a strange visitor; and the railroad crew reaches the important 40-mile mark.
